title: Barstool Pick Em Week 14 Championship Saturday
description:
Big Cat and Hank are live in the Barstool Heartland office and joined by Diggs, Pat Mcafee and CFB gambling expert Shawn Latham AKA the $20 Chef to break down all of the big championship games of the weekend + a call from the alleged King Of The West Coast, Rico Bosco
